high_descs: Turn around and go near the diningtable.
Take the egg from the table.
Turn around and go to the bowl.
Put the egg on the bowl in the cupboard of the table.
Take the bowl with egg from the cupboard of the table.
Turn around and go near the sidetable.
Put the bowl with egg on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Placed the Egg bowl on the SideTable.

high_descs: Head rotate and turn left and turn left to the dining table.
Pick the egg from the dining table.
Turn right and turn left to the drawer.
Put the egg inside the drawer in the bowl.
Pick the bowl from the drawer.
Turn left and turn right to the side table.
Place the bowl on the side table.
anns.task_desc: To place the bowl on the side table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the dresser, then turn left and go all the way down this hallway until you can take a left into a larger room, approaching the circular table ahead.
Pick up the egg from the table.
Return to the room you began in and approach the dresser.
Open the drawer closest to the bed and place the egg into the bowl there.
Pick up the bowl with the egg in it.
Go back to the room you got the egg from and walk past the circular table to the rectangular table with a microwave on it.
Put the bowl down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with an egg in it on a table.
